<plot>This story of the Nazi prison camps in the 1930s deals with the attempts of the Nazi guards to break the spirit of the Communists in concentration camps. The film ends with a large worker's strike looming that makes the escape of Paul possible. Shown in the USA in April of 1939 at the Waldorf Theater in NYC, with Russian dialogue and English titles.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?078253</url></doc>
